{
  "stem": "18802.2",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 16.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "This guy, he wasn't blacklisted, but he was a little bit suspicious, because he was a monarchist.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You know?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "This means, more or less, an enemy of the Nazis.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So anyway, we went both together to this office.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they said, yes, yes, we approve of the sale.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[INAUDIBLE] we are really glad to hear it, yeah?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But I tell you, this Jewish woman gets 30% less from the price you agreed.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So we went down the stairs.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We both signed.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And we went down the stairs.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And his name was [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "So he said, when we were going down, now you think [INAUDIBLE] swine, these pigs.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "He arranged it nicely, that you get less.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "But I tell you before what I told you, I give you.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And I give this 30% black under the table.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "So you have some black money.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "That was, for this man, very dangerous.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And for me, very dangerous to accept and for him to give.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Anyway, two days later he got a letter.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The sale of the house is finally approved, and the price is $130,000.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That mean $30,000 more than he agreed first.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So there was no idea that he give me anything, because he had to make a loan from his father-in-law for the $30,000.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They didn't have the money.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Anyway, he got the house.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And this man did everything, what he could, to be helpful, risking his life.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He was driving me around the last errands, and everything you see.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Because I got permission to take the furniture that was very costly, and the carpets, out of the country.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "No money.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I got an allowance to get three-- the value of three English pounds, approximately, cash.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Yeah?",
      "word_count": 1
    }
  ],
